Future Scope of Work
The output format of each layer is inconsistent. You can use the function API capability of GPT to instruct the output format as per the input request.
The rule framework provided to classify each laptops specification is not exhaustive. You can expand the rules to give a comprehensive context to the LLM.
There are misclassifications in the laptops specifications, even after specifying clear rules for LLM. You can fine-tune an open-source LLM to make its understanding & performance better.
Once the products are extracted, the dialogue flow doesnt allow recalling of product extraction if there is any intent change. You can add another layer to observe any request for a change in the user intent and then use this flag to recall the product extraction based on the updated intent.
As an alternative & simple solution, you can use vector embeddings of each product and compare it with the user intent to find the most relevant products.
You can template this workflow/solution to build a chatbot for any product domain. Note: You must add the relevant domain expertise/rules to give the LLM context understanding.
